Author: teeandcookies
Text: I don’t know if my mum went in my room because she didn’t mention it when I saw her, but it could be my older sister which terrifies me because I know she’ll use it against me and call me a fat pig etc if she does know i ate a lot.

Author: Soggy_Ramen
Text: Is there any other reason for her to suspect it? If not hopefully your mom will just think you're a typical young person with an unhealthy diet and a messy room. It's pretty typical. Try and just stay calm, if you freak out about it that's when she'll be suspicious, but even then she might be suspicious you're smoking weed and have the munchies. I'm honestly just going off what my own parents would have thought.
